Doraboneun geotto waenji geobi na

Eonjena gateun jari

Oneul nan cheoeumeuro
Soljikhan nae maeumeul majuhae
Geoul ape seoneun geotto meomuttae

Jamshi meomulda adeukhi meoreojyeodo

Sojunghan uri iyagi
Jinshimi damgin maeumi
Shigani jina dashi gieokhal su ittamyeon
Malhal su isseulkka
Neodo haengbokhaettago

Neowa ulgo gachi utgo
Gidaehago apahaetji
Modeun geol ssotgo saranghago
Maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

Gipge sangcheo nan jari
Neul gateun sokdoro heulleoganeun shigani

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just incredible in every sense. He is one of the few vocalists who can make your heart flutter and cause a storm of emotions. He manages his deep voice and sweet timbre with such ease that the same part can sound completely different "starting very roughly and ending unrealistically gently". Kyungsoo's unique voice gives each song a unique charm. I'm ready to listen to his voice as much as I want.! Even when Kyungsoo just speaks, he wants to listen and listen to endlessly, such a pleasant voice.

author: @liza_pet
text: EXO is a diamond not only of SM but of the entire K-POP industry. I sincerely apologize, but the visual effects of EXO are too powerful, as soon as they appear on the stage, they capture you with their dazzle, not letting you go until the very end. It's been a whole 11 years, but they simply have no equal in live performances.

author: @liza_pet
text:

has absolutely nothing to do to be so cute. 
I love him madly for such spontaneity, sincerity and absolutely unique vocals that you can listen to endlessly.

text:
As many professional musicians, soloists, idols say, Kyungsoo songs may seem easy only at first glance, but when you start singing you realize how difficult it is. The pure truth is how well Kyungsoo owns his voice with his vocals

author: @liza_pet
text:
Baby Kyungsoo is the cutest, polite, and humble idol in the entire K-POP industry. Although he does not consider himself cute and does not 
like to be called that, but it's the truth and he 
has absolutely nothing to do to be so cute. 
I love him madly for such spontaneity, sincerity and absolutely unique vocals that you can listen to endlessly.

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just incredible in every sense. He is one of the few vocalists who can make your heart flutter and cause a storm of emotions. He manages his deep voice and sweet timbre with such ease that the same part can sound completely different "starting very roughly and ending unrealistically gently". Kyungsoo's unique voice gives each song a unique charm. I'm ready to listen to his voice as much as I want.! Even when Kyungsoo just speaks, he wants to listen and listen to endlessly, such a pleasant voice.

text:
I just love how Kyungsoo dances absolutely 
every movement of his, and in absolutely any choreography so smooth and gentle that it seems as if he does not make any effort everything happens so naturally, of course, 
he is given such plasticity by nature.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Do Kyungsoo just has an unrealistically beautiful face and is literally getting more beautiful every day. He is exactly the kind of person who suits absolutely any style, hairstyle and concept, as evidenced by numerous EXO albums, numerous advertising and numerous acting shots of Kyungsoo, which are so different in a variety 
of roles and images.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Do Kyungsoo is just an incredible person that I will never stop admiring. At first glance, the album, the songs and his vocals may seem simple, but in fact it is not so at all. A large range does not make you a better vocalist yet, because another important role is played by the "technique", which Kyungsoo undoubtedly has great. He has such control over his voice that he makes all the transitions from low to high notes completely smoothly and even seems to make no effort. Quite naturally, during a song, it can change its timbre from incredibly sweet to sexually rude and sound simply amazing in each. Kyungsoo is one of those few vocalists who can make your heart flutter.
/
This album is something unique that Kyungsoo has put his soul into. He himself wrote the lyrics for the title song "Rose", and also took a direct part in writing each song. He learned to play guitar while still serving in the army, studied independently and played each of his songs from the album to record. He has recorded songs in several languages "Korean, English, Spanish" which not everyone does.

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just incredible in every sense. He is one of the few vocalists who can make your heart flutter and cause a storm of emotions. He manages his deep voice and sweet timbre with such ease that the same part can sound completely different "starting very roughly and ending unrealistically gently". Kyungsoo's unique voice gives each song a unique charm. I'm ready to listen to his voice as much as I want.! Even when Kyungsoo just speaks, he wants to listen and listen to endlessly, such a pleasant voice.

author: @liza_pet
text:
EXO is my very first and only favorite band in the entire K-POP industry and baby Kyungsoo "D.O." is my very first and only bias in the entire K-POP industry. Or rather, it was love at first sight, of course all the members are unrealistically talented beauties, but it was baby D.O. who attracted my attention as soon as I saw him 
for the first time.

Sudah lama berlalu

Aku hanya menatap ke depan dan terus berlari 
Mengapa aku begitu takut untuk berbalik
Semua kisah yang ku simpan 
 
Seiring berjalannya waktu, di dalam hatiku

Bahkan hari yang penuh air mata sebanyak hatiku yang mati rasa

Dirimu yang seperti itu, ya, itu tak apa-apa, tak apa-apa 
 
Hari ini, untuk pertama kalinya 
Aku melihat hatiku yang sebenarnya 
Di depan cermin, aku bahkan berdiri dengan begitu ragu 
Lagi, mengapa raut wajahku ini terlihat begitu canggung?
 
Sesuatu yang indah, itu selalu berharga 
Itu selalu tinggal untuk sesaat dan menjauh dengan perlahan 
Itu selalu jelas seperti yang terlihat 
Mata hati memenuhi kehidupan sehari-hari

Andai waktu berlalu dan kau bisa mengingatnya kembali

Bahwa kau juga bahagia

Gaseumi jeoril mankeum nunmulgyeoun naldo
Maeil gachi tteugo jineun taeyanggwa
Jeo dalcheoreom jayeonseure bonae

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron utgo
Gidaehago apahaji
Dashi seollego mudyeojigo
Maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

Sumaneun byeori geuraetteushi
Eonjena gateun jari
Je mokse bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Ne moseub geudaero geurae gwaenchana gwaenchanado

Oneul nan cheoeumeuro
Soljikhan nae maeumeul majuhae
Geoul ape seoneun geotto meomuttae
I pyojeongeun tto wae irido eosaekhae

Areumdaun geon neul sojunghago
Jamshi meomulda adeukhi meoreojyeodo
Neul maju bodeut pyeongbeomhan
Ilsangeul chaeul maeume nun

Geu ane gamchwodun weroumdo
Jamshi meomul su itge hae
Geujeo barabwa
Budeureoun barami bulmyeon
Maeumeul yeoreo jinagal haruya

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron utgo
Gidaehago apahaji
Dashi seollego mudyeojigo
Maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

Sumaneun byeori geuraetteushi
Eonjena gateun jari
Je mokse bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Ne moseub geudaero geurae gwaenchana gwaenchanado

Du sone gadeuk chaewojil chueokdeureun
Sojunghan uri iyagi
Jinshimi damgin maeumi
Shigani jina dashi gieokhal su ittamyeon
Malhal su isseulkka
Neodo haengbokhaettago

Neowa ulgo gachi utgo
Gidaehago apahaetji
Modeun geol ssotgo saranghago
Maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

author: @liza_pet
text: Kyungsoo just has an unrealistically beautiful face and is literally getting more beautiful every day. He is exactly the kind of person who suits absolutely any style, hairstyle and concept, as evidenced by numerous EXO albums, numerous advertising and numerous acting shots of Kyungsoo, which are so different in a variety of roles and images.

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just incredible in every sense. He is one of the few vocalists who can make your heart flutter and cause a storm of emotions. He manages his deep voice and sweet timbre with such ease that the same part can sound completely different "starting very roughly and ending unrealistically gently". Kyungsoo's unique voice gives each song a unique charm. I'm ready to listen to his voice as much as I want.! Even when Kyungsoo just speaks, he wants to listen and listen to endlessly, such a pleasant voice.

author: @kylatoledo6462
text:
"That's Okay"
[Romanized:]

Suthage seuchyeogan
Gamjeongdeure mudyeojineun gamgak
Eonjebuteonga iksukhaejyeobeorin
Maeumeul sumgineun beobdeul

Nan eodijjeume wa itna
Apman bogo dallyeoogiman haetteon
Doraboneun geotto waenji geobi na
Mirwodun yaegideul

Shigani gadeut nae anen
Haengbokhaesseotteon ttaeron
Gaseumi jeoril mankeum nunmulgyeoun naldo
Maeil gachi tteugo jineun taeyanggwa
Jeo dalcheoreom jayeonseure bonae

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron utgo
Gidaehago apahaji
Dashi seollego mudyeojigo
Maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

Sumaneun byeori geuraetteushi
Eonjena gateun jari
Je mokse bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Ne moseub geudaero geurae gwaenchana gwaenchanado

Oneul nan cheoeumeuro
Soljikhan nae maeumeul majuhae
Geoul ape seoneun geotto meomuttae
I pyojeongeun tto wae irido eosaekhae

Areumdaun geon neul sojunghago
Jamshi meomulda adeukhi meoreojyeodo
Neul maju bodeut pyeongbeomhan
Ilsangeul chaeul maeume nun

Geu ane gamchwodun weroumdo
Jamshi meomul su itge hae
Geujeo barabwa
Budeureoun barami bulmyeon
Maeumeul yeoreo jinagal haruya

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron utgo
Gidaehago apahaji
Dashi seollego mudyeojigo
Maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

Sumaneun byeori geuraetteushi
Eonjena gateun jari
Je mokse bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Ne moseub geudaero geurae gwaenchana gwaenchanado

Du sone gadeuk chaewojil chueokdeureun
Sojunghan uri iyagi
Jinshimi damgin maeumi
Shigani jina dashi gieokhal su ittamyeon
Malhal su isseulkka
Neodo haengbokhaettago

Neowa ulgo gachi utgo
Gidaehago apahaetji
Modeun geol ssotgo saranghago
Maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

Malhaji mothal gomingeori
Gipge sangcheo nan jari
Neul gateun sokdoro heulleoganeun shigani
Eonjena geuraetteushi sshiseonaejul teni
Heureudeut sarado geunyang gwaenchana gwaenchanado

text:
Sudah lama berlalu 
Inderaku yang mati rasa dalam perasaan 
Sejak kapankah aku terbiasa dengannya
Cara untuk menyembunyikan perasaanku 
 
Dimanakah aku berada
Aku hanya menatap ke depan dan terus berlari 
Mengapa aku begitu takut untuk berbalik
Semua kisah yang ku simpan 
 
Seiring berjalannya waktu, di dalam hatiku 
Saat-saat aku bahagia dulu 
Bahkan hari yang penuh air mata sebanyak hatiku yang mati rasa 
Setiap hari matahari terbit dan terbenam dengan cara yang sama 
Seperti bulan itu yang terbenam dengan sendirinya 
 
Terkadang aku menangis, terkadang aku tertawa 
Tidakkah berharap itu menyakitkan? 
Aku menjadi berdebar kemudian kembali mati rasa 
Seperti itulah hatiku bereaksi, dengan apa adanya
 
Seperti bintang yang tak terhitung jumlahnya 
Itu selalu ada di tempat yang sama 
Aku akan bersinar terang dengan cahayaku sendiri 
Jangan bersembunyi, aku akan menunjukannya padamu dengan pasti
Dirimu yang seperti itu, ya, itu tak apa-apa, tak apa-apa 
 
Hari ini, untuk pertama kalinya 
Aku melihat hatiku yang sebenarnya 
Di depan cermin, aku bahkan berdiri dengan begitu ragu 
Lagi, mengapa raut wajahku ini terlihat begitu canggung?
 
Sesuatu yang indah, itu selalu berharga 
Itu selalu tinggal untuk sesaat dan menjauh dengan perlahan 
Itu selalu jelas seperti yang terlihat 
Mata hati memenuhi kehidupan sehari-hari
 
Bahkan kesepian yang tersembunyi di dalam hatimu 
Itu bisa tetap berada disana untuk sesaat 
Karna itu, cobalah kau lihat
Saat angin yang lembut berhembus 
Bukalah hatimu, itu adalah hari untuk melaluinya 
 
Terkadang aku menangis, terkadang aku tertawa

Aku menjadi berdebar kemudian kembali mati rasa

Dirimu yang seperti itu, ya, itu tak apa-apa, tak apa-apa 
 
Kenangan yang memenuhi kedua tanganmu
Kisah kita yang berharga 
Sebuah hati yang penuh ketulusan 
Andai waktu berlalu dan kau bisa mengingatnya kembali 
Bisakah kau memberitahuku?
Bahwa kau juga bahagia 
 
Aku menangis dan tertawa bersamamu 
Tidakkah berharap itu menyakitkan? 
Aku mencurahkan semuanya dan mencintaimu 
Seperti itulah hatiku bereaksi, dengan apa adanya
 
Kekhawatiran yang tak terucapkan 
Itu menjadi luka yang kian dalam 
Waktu selalu berlalu dengan kecepatan yang sama 
Selalu seperti itu, itu akan menghapusnya 
Meski hidup mengalir seperti itu, tak apa-apa, tak apa-apa

author: @kyungsoodo3288
text:
A letter from Kyungsoo


Dear ROSE,

How are you, MY LOVE? DAD told me you're worried and sad (sigh). I know how hard it is to be away from each other but DON'T WORRY my training will be over soon and we'll get to see each other gain. If CRYING OUT loud will somehow make you feel comfortable and ease, feel free to do it, THAT'S OKAY, but do it once (tease). Do you remember when you TELL ME WHAT IS LOVE? You give and define all the meanings of love. Then you make me feel it and realize how love defies everything. When I haven't met you, I don't believe in love. But the moment I laid my eyes on you, I know IT'S LOVE. Anyway, if you'd ask me, I'm doing good, I'M FINE. So please, stop worrying. There will be no more GOODBYE SUMMER, I promise. Just remember, I'M GONNA LOVE YOU FOR LIFE.

D.O.

author: @kyukyumberry
text:
Let's sing together~

Suthage seuchyeogan
Gamjeongdeure mudyeojineun gamgak
Eonjebuteonga iksukhaejyeobeorin
Maeumeul sumgineun beobdeul

Nan eodijjeume wa itna
Apman bogo dallyeoogiman haetteon
Doraboneun geotto waenji geobi na
Mirwodun yaegideul

Shigani gadeut nae anen
Haengbokhaesseotteon ttaeron
Gaseumi jeoril mankeum nunmulgyeoun naldo
Maeil gachi tteugo jineun taeyanggwa
Jeo dalcheoreom jayeonseure bonae

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron utgo
Gidaehago apahaji
Dashi seollego mudyeojigo
Maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

Sumaneun byeori geuraetteushi
Eonjena gateun jari
Je mokse bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Ne moseub geudaero geurae gwaenchana gwaenchanado

Oneul nan cheoeumeuro
Soljikhan nae maeumeul majuhae
Geoul ape seoneun geotto meomuttae
I pyojeongeun tto wae irido eosaekhae

Areumdaun geon neul sojunghago
Jamshi meomulda adeukhi meoreojyeodo
Neul maju bodeut pyeongbeomhan
Ilsangeul chaeul maeume nun

Geu ane gamchwodun weroumdo
Jamshi meomul su itge hae
Geujeo barabwa
Budeureoun barami bulmyeon
Maeumeul yeoreo jinagal haruya

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron utgo
Gidaehago apahaji
Dashi seollego mudyeojigo
Maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

Sumaneun byeori geuraetteushi
Eonjena gateun jari
Je mokse bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Ne moseub geudaero geurae gwaenchana gwaenchanado

Du sone gadeuk chaewojil chueokdeureun
Sojunghan uri iyagi
Jinshimi damgin maeumi
Shigani jina dashi gieokhal su ittamyeon
Malhal su isseulkka
Neodo haengbokhaettago

Neowa ulgo gachi utgo
Gidaehago apahaetji
Modeun geol ssotgo saranghago
Maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

Malhaji mothal gomingeori
Gipge sangcheo nan jari
Neul gateun sokdoro heulleoganeun shigani
Eonjena geuraetteushi sshiseonaejul teni
Heureudeut sarado geunyang gwaenchana gwaenchanado

text: This song makes me shed tears every time I listen to it. Being an EXOL saved me from anxiety and overthinking. Most of the time I pity myself because I don't have friends. We are one, EXO Saranghaja!

author: @miamoresoo2741
text:
Wrote this poem for you almost a year back. Posting it again, now that I can actually see you while you are singing this soulful song. 
.
.
You came into my life 
During my most troubled times
When darkness became my ally
And my soul sought for some light

As my mind wandered around
Hopelessly lost in despair
You came like a ray of sunshine
Spreading your warmth the way I desired

Your voice became my sweet lullaby
Your laughter became my safe haven
The more I heard and learned about you
The calmer my aching heart became

Now, you give me hope, you give me light
You give me the strength to feel alive
You are my dream, a breath of fresh air
One thing I never knew my life required

Dear international friends,

Sorry for posting a message here! ğŸ™

suthage seuchyeogan
gamjeongdeure mudyeojineun gamgak
eonjebuteonga iksukhaejyeobeorin
maeumeul sumgineun beobdeul
nan eodijjeume wa itna
apman bogo dallyeoogiman haetteon
doraboneun geotto waenji geobi na
mirwodun yaegideul

shigani gadeut nae anen
haengbokhaesseotteon ttaeron
gaseumi jeoril mankeum nunmulgyeoun naldo
maeil gachi tteugo jineun taeyanggwa
jeo dalcheoreom jayeonseure bonae

ttaeron ulgo ttaeron utgo
gidaehago apahaji
dashi seollego mudyeojigo
maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

sumaneun byeori geuraetteushi
eonjena gateun jari
je mokse bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
ne moseub geudaero geurae gwaenchana gwaenchanado

oneul nan cheoeumeuro
soljikhan nae maeumeul majuhae
geoul ape seoneun geotto meomuttae
i pyojeongeun tto wae irido eosaekhae

areumdaun geon neul sojunghago
jamshi meomulda adeukhi meoreojyeodo
neul maju bodeut pyeongbeomhan
ilsangeul chaeul maeume nun

geu ane gamchwodun weroumdo
jamshi meomul su itge hae
geujeo barabwa
budeureoun barami bulmyeon
maeumeul yeoreo jinagal haruya

ttaeron ulgo ttaeron utgo
gidaehago apahaji
dashi seollego mudyeojigo
maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

sumaneun byeori geuraetteushi
eonjena gateun jari
je mokse bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
ne moseub geudaero geurae gwaenchana gwaenchanado

du sone gadeuk chaewojil chueokdeureun
sojunghan uri iyagi
jinshimi damgin maeumi
shigani jina dashi gieokhal su ittamyeon
malhal su isseulkka
neodo haengbokhaettago

neowa ulgo gachi utgo
gidaehago apahaetji
modeun geol ssotgo saranghago
maeumi ganeun daero itneun geudaero

malhaji mothal gomingeori
gipge sangcheo nan jari
neul gateun sokdoro heulleoganeun shigani
eonjena geuraetteushi sshiseonaejul teni
heureudeut sarado geunyang gwaenchana gwaenchanado

author: @iamchosennotforsaken5421
text:
life is short and tomorrow is not promised to anyone, anywhere. some people die in their sleep, i am telling this for us to realize that there really is an urgency for change of heart. i don't want anyone else to be in danger of losing their own soul just because no one told them about this. 

please let us all stop involving ourselves in magic, new age, chakras, divinations, spiritualism, witchcraft, law of attraction, astral projection,tarot, etc. these are all demonic. it brings good to you because it wants you to stay until your soul is already tied to it. it's wolves in sheep's clothing! 

if this life we have is temporary, there is eternal life waiting on the other side. same thing, if there is one death on earth then there's eternal death. it's either heaven or hell and it's real, no doubt, just look around and you'll see the difference. if we were to all die tonight where would you be after death? accept Jesus as your Lord and Savior now, that'll be the best decision you've ever made

we don't just live to die, Romans 6:23 "For the wages of sin is death, but the gift of God is eternal life in Christ Jesus our Lord." we die because all of us sinned and that's one enough reason why we need to get right with God. 

REPENT, we all sinned against GOD and after asking for forgiveness, we need to turn away from it. 

ACCEPT JESUS AS YOUR LORD AND SAVIOR, we all will die and all will be judged, JESUS died on the cross as wages for our sins and if we don't accept it, we will die for our own in the eternal lake of fire. 

BE BORN AGAIN, im not talking about religion, its about laying down your past self and making your identity and life new through and for JESUS. 

GOD loves us all and we must get right back with HIM. this world will perish, all people will die, but GOD is eternal and stop the doubt. believe to see! 

God bless you all, brothers and sisters!

author: @rosedyo
text:
I love reading all the long comments praising him.

I have known Kyungsoo since 100dmp and I will continue to brag that fact to the end. After a year since 100dmp, I kept looking for Kyungsoo and Exo by myself, I finally fell in love with them. I wasnâ€™t so interested in kpop before, thatâ€™s why I needed a year to search and understand about them. It was like a miracle, he took me to Exo without I realized it. 

Kyungsoo is not like a typical k-idol. My first impression of him was that he didn't do too much make-up, didn't do aegyo, his voice was so deep and his voice I couldn't describe it, it just sounded very good to me. I donâ€™t complain about anyone else but he is just unique which makes me attracted more to him. Once I got to know Exo, despite having different characters, I love them all. Their vocals are incomparable. They continue to improve every year.

Exo is my first and last idol.  Please stay together until the end. Can't wait for Exo comeback! And ofcos D.O. first solo!

author: @idkwhoiam3177
text:
Not an exo-l but I genuinely love and admire this guy. Honestly speaking, I never saw an idol with such personality.  He is always so humble, honest and leads a simple life. The interesting part about him is that he only does things that he wants to do, doesn't give a fc*k about what others want him to do ( he shaved his head for a role, right?) Not everyone has this kind of courage! Not to mention, hes such a well-rounded artist too. His vocal tone is the best one for me in whole kpop. His tone and way of singing gives off western rnb vibe. I would definitely love to hear more songs from him.
P.S: exo-ls really should be proud bcoz they have such an amazing person as their idol.

author: @ItinakdangAsulTV
text:
To be honest, I went in to denial stage before becoming an EXO fan (EXO-L).

It's D.O. who introduced me to the group anyway. I've known him first as an actor but I fell in love with him as a singer. Did I fall for his acting skills? Yes! BUT I fell deeper for his voice and his personality. You read it right, His unique traits pulled me closer to him. Indeed he's totally unique. I can see and feel his sincerity. You can see through his eyes how genuine he is. He's that person who you'd feel safe around. Someone who'll remind you to keep going when you want to give up. He's that kind of person who'll always be behind you to cheer you up when you feel so down. Something like that. I saw that from his personality. He's one of a kind. You'll see the truthfullness in his eyes. I'm just so lucky to have finally have this song of him to listen to. 

So whatever happens, I'll always support this guy 'coz you can never find someone like him again.

text:
Lirik dan terjemahan bahasa indonesia :

Suthage seuchyeogan gamjeongdeure mudyeojineun gamgak
Tekanan yang muncul karena terlalu banyak perasaan yang menumpuk

Eonjebuteonga iksukhaejyeobeorin maeumeul sumgineun beopdeul
Entah sejak kapan aku mulai terbiasa menyembunyikan perasaanku

Nan eodijjeume wa issna apman bogo dallyeoogiman haessdeon
Entah kemana sebenarnya tujuanku yang ku lakukan hanya terus berlari kedepan

Doraboneun geosdo waenji geobi na mirwodun yaegideul
Dengan perasaan takut untuk menoleh kebelakang kepada cerita kita yang tertunda

Sigani gadeut nae anen haengbokhaesseossdeon

Ttaeron gaseumi jeoril mankeum nunmulgyeoun naldo

Maeil gati tteugo jineun taeyanggwa
Aku menghabiskan waktuku seperti itu setiap hari

Jeo dalcheoreom jayeonseure bonae
Seperti matahari dan bulan yang bergantian dengan alami

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron usgo
Terkadang menangis, terkadang tertawa

Gidaehago apahaji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Dasi seollego mudyeojigo
Merasa bersemangat lagi, namun juga merasa bosan

Maeumi ganeun daero issneun geudaero
Sama Seperti yang hatimu rasakan

Sumanheun byeori geuraessdeusi eonjena gateun jari
Seperti bintang-bintang yang selalu berada di tempat yang sama

Je moksui bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Aku akan terus bersinar terang dengan cahayaku sendiri

Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Jangan sembunyikan apapun, tunjukkanlah padaku dengan nyaman

Ne moseup geudaero geurae gwaenchanha gwaenchanhado
Walaupun kamu menampilkan dirimu yang sebenarnya, itu tidak apa-apa

Oneul nan cheoeumeuro
Hari ini untuk pertama kalinya

Soljikhan nae maeumeul majuhae
Aku bertatapan dengan hatiku yang jujur

Geoul ape seoneun geosdo meomusdae
Aku berdiri didepan cermin

I pyojeongeun tto wae irido eosaekhae
Namun entah mengapa, ekspresi lagi-lagi tampak canggung

Areumdaun geon neul sojunghago
Hal-hal indah yang selalu berharga

Jamsi meomulda adeukhi meoreojyeodo
Walaupun akan berlalu, setidaknya mereka pernah ada sedikit lebih lama

Neul maju bodeut pyeongbeomhan ilsangeul chaeul maeumui nun
Hari-hariku selalu berjalan dengan normal

Geu ane gamchwodun oeroumdo jamsi meomul su issge hae
Biarkan rasa sepi itu hadir hanya untuk waktu yang singkat

Geujeo barabwa budeureoun barami bulmyeon
Perhatikanlah, jika angin lembut mulai berhembus menyelimuti

Maeumeul yeoreo jinagal haruya
Saat itu adalah hari yang tepat untuk membuka hatimu

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron usgo
Terkadang menangis, terkadang tertawa

Gidaehago apahaji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Dasi seollego mudyeojigo
Merasa bersemangat lagi, namun juga merasa bosan

Je moksui bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni

Walaupun kamu menampilkan dirimu yang sebenarnya, itu tidak apa-apa

Du sone gadeuk chaewojil chueokdeureun
Kenang-kenangan yang terkumul oleh kedua tangan kita

Sojunghan uri iyagi
Kisah kita yang berharga

Jinsimi damgin maeumi
Dan hati yang penuh ketulusan

Sigani jina dasi gieokhal su issdamyeon
Jika seiring waktu berjalan kamu masih mengingat semua itu

Malhal su isseulkka neodo haengbokhaessdago
Bolehkah aku mengira bahwa selama ini kamu juga merasa bahagia

Neowa ulgo gati usgo
Menangis dan tertawa bersama

Gidaehago apahaessji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Modeun geol ssotgo saranghago
Melupakan segalanya dan saling mencintai

Maeumi ganeun daero issneun geudaero

Malhaji moshal gomingeori

Gipge sangcheo nan jari

Neul gateun sokdoro heulleoganeun sigani
Waktu akan selalu berjalan dengan kecepatan yang sama

Eonjena geuraessdeusi ssiseonaejul teni

text:
Suthage seuchyeogan gamjeongdeure mudyeojineun gamgak
Tekanan yang muncul karena terlalu banyak perasaan yang menumpuk

Eonjebuteonga iksukhaejyeobeorin maeumeul sumgineun beopdeul
Entah sejak kapan aku mulai terbiasa menyembunyikan perasaanku

Nan eodijjeume wa issna apman bogo dallyeoogiman haessdeon
Entah kemana sebenarnya tujuanku yang ku lakukan hanya terus berlari kedepan

Doraboneun geosdo waenji geobi na mirwodun yaegideul
Dengan perasaan takut untuk menoleh kebelakang kepada cerita kita yang tertunda

Sigani gadeut nae anen haengbokhaesseossdeon

Ttaeron gaseumi jeoril mankeum nunmulgyeoun naldo
Terkadang aku juga merasa sedih

Maeil gati tteugo jineun taeyanggwa
Aku menghabiskan waktuku seperti itu setiap hari

Jeo dalcheoreom jayeonseure bonae
Seperti matahari dan bulan yang bergantian dengan alami

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron usgo
Terkadang menangis, terkadang tertawa

Gidaehago apahaji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Dasi seollego mudyeojigo
Merasa bersemangat lagi, namun juga merasa bosan

Maeumi ganeun daero issneun geudaero
Sama Seperti yang hatimu rasakan

Sumanheun byeori geuraessdeusi eonjena gateun jari
Seperti bintang-bintang yang selalu berada di tempat yang sama

Je moksui bicheuro hwanhage bichul teni
Aku akan terus bersinar terang dengan cahayaku sendiri

Sumgiji malgo neoreul boyeojullae pyeonhi
Jangan sembunyikan apapun, tunjukkanlah padaku dengan nyaman

Ne moseup geudaero geurae gwaenchanha gwaenchanhado
Walaupun kamu menampilkan dirimu yang sebenarnya, itu tidak apa-apa

Oneul nan cheoeumeuro
Hari ini untuk pertama kalinya

Soljikhan nae maeumeul majuhae
Aku bertatapan dengan hatiku yang jujur

Geoul ape seoneun geosdo meomusdae
Aku berdiri didepan cermin

I pyojeongeun tto wae irido eosaekhae
Namun entah mengapa, ekspresi lagi-lagi tampak canggung

Areumdaun geon neul sojunghago
Hal-hal indah yang selalu berharga

Jamsi meomulda adeukhi meoreojyeodo
Walaupun akan berlalu, setidaknya mereka pernah ada sedikit lebih lama

Neul maju bodeut pyeongbeomhan ilsangeul chaeul maeumui nun
Hari-hariku selalu berjalan dengan normal

Geu ane gamchwodun oeroumdo jamsi meomul su issge hae
Biarkan rasa sepi itu hadir hanya untuk waktu yang singkat

Geujeo barabwa budeureoun barami bulmyeon
Perhatikanlah, jika angin lembut mulai berhembus menyelimuti

Maeumeul yeoreo jinagal haruya
Saat itu adalah hari yang tepat untuk membuka hatimu

Ttaeron ulgo ttaeron usgo
Terkadang menangis, terkadang tertawa

Gidaehago apahaji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Walaupun kamu menampilkan dirimu yang sebenarnya, itu tidak apa-apa

Du sone gadeuk chaewojil chueokdeureun
Kenang-kenangan yang terkumul oleh kedua tangan kita

Sojunghan uri iyagi
Kisah kita yang berharga

Jinsimi damgin maeumi
Dan hati yang penuh ketulusan

Sigani jina dasi gieokhal su issdamyeon
Jika seiring waktu berjalan kamu masih mengingat semua itu

Malhal su isseulkka neodo haengbokhaessdago
Bolehkah aku mengira bahwa selama ini kamu juga merasa bahagia

Neowa ulgo gati usgo
Menangis dan tertawa bersama

Gidaehago apahaessji
Berharap dan tersakiti

Modeun geol ssotgo saranghago
Melupakan segalanya dan saling mencintai

Maeumi ganeun daero issneun geudaero
Sama seperti yang hati kita rasakan

Malhaji moshal gomingeori
Sebuah kegelisahan yang tidak bisa diutarakan

Gipge sangcheo nan jari
Sebuah luka yang dalam

Neul gateun sokdoro heulleoganeun sigani
Waktu akan selalu berjalan dengan kecepatan yang sama

Eonjena geuraessdeusi ssiseonaejul teni
Suatu saat nanti, aku akan menghapus semua lukamu

Heureudeut sarado geunyang gwaenchanha gwaenchanhado
